BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 148.8 610 Td (IF METHODS EXPLAINED) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 598 m 382 598 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 575 Td (WHAT IS INTERMITTENT FASTING?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 560 Td (An eating pattern that cycles between fasting and eating windows.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 545 Td (It's about WHEN you eat, not necessarily WHAT you eat.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 530 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 515 Td (POPULAR METHODS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 500 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 485 Td (16:8 METHOD \(most popular for beginners\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 470 Td (Fast 16 hours, eat within 8-hour window) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 455 Td (Example: Eat 12pm-8pm, fast 8pm-12pm) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 440 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 425 Td (18:6 METHOD \(intermediate\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 410 Td (Fast 18 hours, eat within 6-hour window) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (Example: Eat 1pm-7pm, fast 7pm-1pm) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 380 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 365 Td (20:4 METHOD \(advanced\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 350 Td (Fast 20 hours, eat within 4-hour window) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 335 Td (Example: Eat 3pm-7pm, fast 7pm-3pm) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 320 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 305 Td (OMAD - One Meal A Day \(advanced\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 290 Td (Eat one large meal, fast the remaining 23 hours) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 275 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 260 Td (START WITH 16:8 and work up as your body adapts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 245 Td (Most people see results with 16:8 alone.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
