BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 145.44 610 Td (GETTING STARTED GUIDE) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 598 m 382 598 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 575 Td (WEEK 1: Ease into it) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 560 Td (- Start by pushing breakfast 1-2 hours later each day) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 545 Td (- Stop eating 2-3 hours before bed) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 530 Td (- Drink water, black coffee, or plain tea during fasting) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 515 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 500 Td (WEEK 2: Find your window) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 485 Td (- Settle into your chosen eating window) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 470 Td (- Notice energy patterns and adjust timing) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 455 Td (- Eat nutritious meals \(don't binge during eating window\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 440 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 425 Td (DURING FASTING, YOU CAN HAVE:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 410 Td (- Water \(add lemon/electrolytes if needed\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (- Black coffee \(no cream, sugar, or sweetener\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 380 Td (- Plain tea \(green, herbal, black\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 365 Td (- Sparkling water) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 350 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 335 Td (DURING EATING WINDOW, FOCUS ON:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 320 Td (- Protein at every meal) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 305 Td (- Vegetables and fiber) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 290 Td (- Healthy fats) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 275 Td (- Adequate calories \(don't under-eat!\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 260 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 245 Td (STOP FASTING IF: you feel dizzy, faint, nauseous beyond the) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 230 Td (first week of adjustment, or have a medical condition.) Tj ET

