BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 530 Td (- Bone broth + chicken + rice) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 515 Td (- Smoothie with protein powder + greens) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 500 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 485 Td (COMMON QUESTIONS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 470 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 455 Td (Q: Won't I lose muscle?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 440 Td (A: No, if you eat adequate protein \(0.7-1g per lb bodyweight\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 425 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 410 Td (Q: Can I exercise while fasting?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (A: Yes! Many people train fasted. Listen to your body.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 380 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 365 Td (Q: What if I'm hungry?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 350 Td (A: Hunger comes in waves. Drink water. It passes in 15-20 min.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 335 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 320 Td (Q: Can I do IF every day?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 305 Td (A: Most people do. Some prefer 5 days on, 2 off.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 290 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 275 Td (Q: Will it slow my metabolism?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 260 Td (A: No. Short-term fasting can actually increase metabolic rate.) Tj ET

